  "The widespread deforestation occurring in the Amazon rainforest due to agricultural land clearing": "",
  "The increasing acidification of ocean waters caused by dissolved carbon dioxide concentrations": "",
  "Global climate change resulting from rising levels of CO2 and other greenhouse gas emissions": "",
