  "Only the local wildlife populations in the immediate vicinity of the contaminated industrial site": "",
  "Only the geological processes responsible for the natural formation and composition of the underlying soil": "",
  "Only the economic productivity and financial output of the factory that formerly operated at the location": "",
  "This scenario illustrates environmental injustice, where toxic waste sites and pollution sources are disproportionately located near low-income and minority communities, creating unequal health burdens.": "",
